00:53.860 --> 00:55.927
Coming!

00:55.929 --> 00:57.294
You're going with Rachel?

00:57.296 --> 00:59.163
<i>Don't tell me you're jealous.</i>

00:59.165 --> 01:01.966
You must be joking.
She's ugly.

01:01.968 --> 01:05.370
- Now!
- Coming!

01:05.372 --> 01:07.203
<i>I'll send you a selfie
from the Chelsea game.</i>

01:07.205 --> 01:08.774
<i>See you.</i>

01:25.656 --> 01:27.824
No, Mia,
don't do that.

01:27.826 --> 01:29.624
